{"tid":1872773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情爆不完!  中国四川爆H5N6亞型禽流感「可能傳人」","createTime":"2020-02-10T08:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T09:33:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0fa24434be60cbdee6ba12772008b06dec528c","tid":1872773,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，繼中國湖南於2日爆發H5N1亞型高致病性禽流感疫情，共撲殺1萬7828隻家禽。昨日中國官方再公布四川省南充市西充縣的養殖場爆發H5N6亞型高致病性禽流感疫情，農業管理單位已緊急撲殺2261隻家禽。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國農業農村部新聞辦公室於9日發布，經國家禽流感參考實驗室確診，四川省南充市西充縣有養殖場爆發H5N6亞型高致病性禽流感疫情，養殖場飼養家禽共2497隻，發病死亡1840隻，禽鳥死亡率破七成。當局表示疫情發生後，已緊急撲殺家禽2261隻。<br />\n<br />\n根據我國疾管署 規範，此次在四川爆發的H5N6亞型禽流感，曾在2018年中國廣東省傳出病例，雖動物傳人的可能性罕見，不過正因人類感染禽流感病毒的情況並不常見，因此人體對該病毒的免疫力極低，甚至沒有免疫力。一旦禽流感病毒具備適應能力，或從人類病毒中獲取某些基因，以致能輕易地在人與人之間傳播，便會出現流感大流行，對人類疾病嚴重度高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3063076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3063076&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=309f6d11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3063076&h=8993ce64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3063076</a>"},{"pid":"d6886bc627c6c1a13498d701237ed819af982437","tid":1872773,"uid":338097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"禽流感好似都傳左段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e7a4cdfacd96ec73b17b9dcf2c7814c4d30eac","tid":1872773,"uid":58294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"姐係可以傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273cf0794a8b3a3ca73f3c95f0800318430d5d08","tid":1872773,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"人類要進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72854b006fa0e7cea23eabbc9815fd06dbb9249d","tid":1872773,"uid":252262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NcKjYCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcKjYCv.jpg&h=570e772c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8d8e95d2baef2db31abce29485e51a32dbb90d4","tid":1872773,"uid":291947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"不要可能，而係H5N6一定要人傳人"},{"pid":"9c62c503d0177bab706cac8878eef225b5a3c587","tid":1872773,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}